nodes.text: Vozburk was a concept found in S'kytri mythology. It referred to an all-out conflict between the Windborn and the ground-dwelling demons of Skye. By the time of the Clone Wars, that term had become archaic in S'kytric. However, it was used as the code name of an attack plan designed to defeat the genetics terrorist Zeta Magnus, who had enslaved the Windborn.
